    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK679">
<l>naṭṭārkku nalla ceyaliṉ viraintatē</l>
<l>yoṭṭārai oṭṭik koḷal</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>One should rather hasten to secure the alliance of the foes (of one's foes) than perform good offices to one's friends</l>
            </lg>
